question: Give me restaurants and cafes that serve Italian cuisine.
sql_query1:
SELECT Restaurants.Name 
FROM Restaurants
WHERE (Restaurants.Food_Service = "Restaurant" OR Restaurants.Food_Service = "Café") AND Restaurants.Cuisine = "Italian"
sql_query2:
SELECT Restaurants.Name 
FROM Restaurants
WHERE Restaurants.Food_Service = "Restaurant" OR Restaurants.Food_Service = "Café" AND Restaurants.Cuisine = "Italian"
interpretation1: What restaurants serve Italian cuisine and what cafes serve the same cuisine?
interpretation2: List all restaurants and also list cafes that serve Italian cuisine.
